          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/product-as-a-channel.astro:8k9455">Contenu qui s'adapte à l'état du produit, à son statut de propriété et à son stade du cycle de vie.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-700 font-medium" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/product-as-a-channel.astro:card-list-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/product-as-a-channel.astro:ddzunr"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Parcours tenant compte de la propriété</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/product-as-a-channel.astro:ddzunq"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Visibilité sur le suivi après-vente</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/product-as-a-channel.astro:ddzunp"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Comportement mesurable</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      
    
  



  <!-- Visual Separator Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-slate-950 text-white relative overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/product-as-a-channel.astro:evidence-section">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-30" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/product-as-a-channel.astro:img-container">
      <img crossorigin="anonymous"
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1770739982427-3169499c332e?auto=format&w=1200&q=80"
        srcset="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1770739982427-3169499c332e?auto=format&w=320&q=80 320w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1770739982427-3169499c332e?auto=format&w=480&q=80 480w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1770739982427-3169499c332e?auto=format&w=640&q=80 640w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1770739982427-3169499c332e?auto=format&w=768&q=80 768w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1770739982427-3169499c332e?auto=format&w=1024&q=80 1024w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1770739982427-3169499c332e?auto=format&w=1280&q=80 1280w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1770739982427-3169499c332e?auto=format&w=1920&q=80 1920w"
        sizes="100vw"
        alt="Digital interaction concept" class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/product-as-a-channel.astro:kwsdk2" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-950 via-slate-950/80 to-transparent" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/product-as-a-channel.astro:8ygl33"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/product-as-a-channel.astro:evidence-content">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/product-as-a-channel.astro:evidence-grid-wrap">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-16 text-center" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/product-as-a-channel.astro:evidence-h">Le produit devient une interface.</h2>
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/product-as-a-channel.astro:evidence-grid">
           <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-white/10 shadow-2xl" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/product-as-a-channel.astro:evidence-box-1">
             <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/product-as-a-channel.astro:8ygl34">
               <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/20 flex items-center justify-center" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/product-as-a-channel.astro:8ygl35">
                 <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-layout"><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="3" x2="21" y1="9" y2="9"/><line x1="9" x2="9" y1="21" y2="9"/></svg>
               </div>
               <h4 class="text-blue-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/product-as-a-channel.astro:evidence-label-1">Le résultat</h4>
             </div>
             <ul class="space-y-6" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/product-as-a-channel.astro:evidence-list-1">
